  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 7 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "7 more people who tried to flee the country were arrested",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Over the past few days, the number of people going abroad illegally by boat has been increasing.",
        "In that way, seven more Sri Lankans who tried to flee the country illegally by boat yesterday evening have been arrested.",
        "The Sri Lankan Navy said that they were arrested during the encirclement that was carried out in the Thalaimannar sea area yesterday evening."
      ],
